    "dhp274:1": "Eseva → esova (bj) ",
    "dhp275:3": "Akkhāto vo → akkhāto ve (bj, pts1ed, pts2ed) ",
    "dhp275:4": "sallakantanaṁ → sallasanthanaṁ (bj, pts1ed, pts2ed); sallasatthanaṁ (sya-all) ",
    "dhp280:3": "Saṁsannasaṅkappamano → asampannasaṅkappamano (mr) ",
    "dhp281:2": "nākusalaṁ kayirā → akusalaṁ na kayirā (bj, sya-all, km, pts1ed, pts2ed) ",
    "dhp282:1": "jāyatī → jāyati (pts1ed); jāyate (katthaci) ",
    "dhp284:3": "Paṭibaddhamanova → paṭibandhamanova (mr) ",
    "dhp284:4": "khīrapakova → khīrapānova (bj) "
  },
